</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2008-03-26</span></span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARandy+David&amp;rft.btitle=David+v.+Arroyo%2C+G.R.+No.+171396%2C+3+May+2006&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.supremecourt.gov.ph%2Fjurisprudence%2F2006%2Fmay2006%2FG.R.%2520No.%2520171396.htm&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Philippine Daily Inquirer: June 26, 2009, front page</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Randy_David&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><span class=\"citation web\">Marcelo, Pepper. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070926215829/http://www.planetphilippines.com/archives/2005/sep1-15-05/current/features_current/feature2.html\">\"The Wisdom of Randy David\"</a>. www.planetphilippines.com. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.planetphilippines.com/archives/2005/sep1-15-05/current/features_current/feature2.html\">the original</a> on 2007-09-26<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2007-06-27</span></span>.</span><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARandy+David&amp;rft.aufirst=Pepper&amp;rft.aulast=Marcelo&amp;rft.au=Marcelo%2C+Pepper&amp;rft.btitle=The+Wisdom+of+Randy+David&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.planetphilippines.com%2Farchives%2F2005%2Fsep1-15-05%2Fcurrent%2Ffeat